        What to Expect When Selling in Cannon Hill
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Cannon Hill sits between Morningside and Murarrie in Brisbane's inner east. Families are the dominant buyer and competition for well-presented homes is consistent.
      </p>
